content:
Gain more control and flexibility when you work with financial account FlexCard components, such as FSCFinancialAccountDetails, FSCFinancialAccountsSummary, and FSCFinancialAccountTransactionDetails. Model your customerâ€™s financial account information in the FlexCard components by using Financial Account and the related objects that are available either in the Financial Services Cloud managed package or in the Financial Account Management Standard Objects data model.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.

Who: To use this feature, users need the Industry Service Excellence and OmniStudio Admin permission sets.

How: To use Financial Account and related standard objects in the financial account FlexCard components, from Setup, find and select Financial Account Settings, and then turn on Financial Account Management Standard Objects.
title: Financial Services Cloud Release Notes
